reviewText: ...this video is sick. it's the best of the Florida Skeleton crew, and others. it was obviously made by a video editing genius. i checked out all the secret parts and watched all the extras. this video is a true work of art. all the skating is amazing and unique. 80's joe and The Dango have my favorite parts. also the music is right on for enhancing the visual experience. it is a must have for a modern skateboarder's video library.
